title: 236. Q&AF: Price Of Entrepreneurship, Starting Age In Business & Evolving Purpose
itunes:title: 236. Q&AF: Price Of Entrepreneurship, Starting Age In Business & Evolving Purpose
description: In today's episode, Andy answers your questions on whether a 19-year-old version of himself would work for the companies he's built or create a brand new business from scratch, the advantages & disadvantages of your actual age when starting a business, and if your purpose can change as you grow over time.
